Preheat oven to 350 degrees F. Brown sausage with mushrooms in large skillet; drain. Return to skillet. Add stuffing mix, carrots and hot water; stir just until moistened. Set aside. Spoon stuffing mixture evenly into hen cavities; close openings with skewers. Place hens, breast sides up, in shallow roasting pan. Brush with oil. Bake 1 hour; spoon jelly over hens. Bake an additional 10 min. or until hens are cooked through (180 degrees F).